{"time":0,"type":"sentence","start":0,"end":109,"value":"let’s take a quiet, thoughtful moment to explore the essence of the number 7, your Heart’s Desire Number."}
{"time":5955,"type":"sentence","start":110,"end":252,"value":"This number holds something so special—your deepest cravings when it comes to love, the kind that brings peace and fulfillment to your soul."}
{"time":13385,"type":"sentence","start":253,"end":304,"value":"At the very core of your heart, you long for depth."}
{"time":16515,"type":"sentence","start":305,"end":385,"value":"You want a love that goes beyond the surface, something meaningful and profound."}
{"time":21082,"type":"sentence","start":386,"end":545,"value":"You crave a partner who shares your curiosity about life, someone who is just as eager as you are to explore the spiritual and intellectual dimensions of love."}
{"time":29812,"type":"sentence","start":546,"end":705,"value":"Your heart seeks a relationship that feels enlightening, where both of you can grow together in a way that feels like you’ve found a sanctuary in each other."}
{"time":37692,"type":"sentence","start":706,"end":798,"value":"I can see that you’re naturally drawn to partners who are thoughtful, introspective souls."}
{"time":42760,"type":"sentence","start":799,"end":879,"value":"They reflect your own values—seeking depth, meaning, and wisdom in all things."}
{"time":47790,"type":"sentence","start":880,"end":1042,"value":"What truly fulfills you is a relationship where you and your partner can explore life’s mysteries together, sharing your insights, and learning from each other."}
{"time":55995,"type":"sentence","start":1043,"end":1157,"value":"It’s a bond that feels rich and inspiring, where every conversation and moment together deepens your connection."}
{"time":62075,"type":"sentence","start":1158,"end":1309,"value":"And, dear heart, I know that you yearn for a love that nurtures your sense of wisdom, a relationship where you can express your true self without fear."}
{"time":70142,"type":"sentence","start":1310,"end":1389,"value":"You seek a love that’s reflective, insightful, and always encouraging growth."}
{"time":74935,"type":"sentence","start":1390,"end":1498,"value":"You want a partner who sees the world as you do—with wonder, curiosity, and a desire to understand it all."}
{"time":81577,"type":"sentence","start":1499,"end":1642,"value":"Together, you’ll create something that goes beyond the ordinary—a love that’s built on shared understanding and a desire to keep growing."}
{"time":88895,"type":"sentence","start":1643,"end":1680,"value":"So, listen to these desires, my dear."}
{"time":92062,"type":"sentence","start":1681,"end":1785,"value":"Nurture them, for they are guiding you toward a love that aligns with the deepest truths of who you are."}
{"time":97280,"type":"sentence","start":1786,"end":1924,"value":"Your heart knows exactly what it seeks, and in time, it will lead you to a love that resonates with the wisdom and depth you carry within."}
